entries.journal_entry_description: Find all three Tusken relics for Srimaur
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Remove the Krayt Head. Try not to be discovered.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Find the three relics: Chieftain's Skull, Krayt Skull, and the Ghastly Baton.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Find Srimaur in Mos Espa. Tell him what happened in the cave.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: Return to Srimaur with the relics
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Warn the Militia Leader of the impending invasion.
